&lt;p&gt;网友&lt;strong&gt;@&lt;span&gt;除了我全部是猪&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;提问：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote class=&quot;js_blockquote_wrap&quot; data-type=&quot;2&quot; data-url=&quot;&quot; data-author-name=&quot;&quot; data-content-utf8-length=&quot;92&quot; data-source-title=&quot;&amp;#x9664;&amp;#x4E86;&amp;#x6211;&amp;#x5168;&amp;#x90E8;&amp;#x662F;&amp;#x732A;&quot; readability=&quot;5&quot;&gt;
&lt;section class=&quot;js_blockquote_digest&quot; readability=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;@和菜头 刚刚逛超市，一位大妈看到我购物车里的可乐，过来跟我科普，说她在朋友圈看到有科学家做实验，给鱼灌可乐，然后鱼就死了还发黑，劝我不要喝。场面一度很尴尬，再碰见类似科普该怎么回答她？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;blockquote_info js_blockquote_source&quot; data-json=&quot;%7B%22type%22%3A%22out%22%2C%22source%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22digest%22%3A%22%22%2C%22digestLen%22%3A92%2C%22text%22%3A%22%40%E5%92%8C%E8%8F%9C%E5%A4%B4%E5%88%9A%E5%88%9A%E9%80%9B%E8%B6%85%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E4%BD%8D%E5%A4%A7%E5%A6%88%E7%9C%8B%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E8%B4%AD%E7%89%A9%E8%BD%A6%E9%87%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AF%E4%B9%90%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%87%E6%9D%A5%E8%B7%9F%E6%88%91%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%B4%E5%A5%B9%E5%9C%A8%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B%E5%9C%88%E7%9C%8B%E5%88%B0%E6%9C%89%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E5%81%9A%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%99%E9%B1%BC%E7%81%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%B9%90%EF%BC%8C%E7%84%B6%E5%90%8E%E9%B1%BC%E5%B0%B1%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%86%E8%BF%98%E5%8F%91%E9%BB%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%8A%9D%E6%88%91%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%96%9D%E3%80%82%E5%9C%BA%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%E5%BE%88%E5%B0%B4%E5%B0%AC%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%8D%E7%A2%B0%E8%A7%81%E7%B1%BB%E4%BC%BC%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E8%AF%A5%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%9B%9E%E7%AD%94%E5%A5%B9%EF%BC%9F%22%2C%22article%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22hasReportOverSize%22%3Afalse%2C%22from%22%3A%22%E9%99%A4%E4%BA%86%E6%88%91%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E6%98%AF%E7%8C%AA%22%7D&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;blockquote_other&quot;&gt;除了我全部是猪&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
